{"tid":1162792,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟落雨同炒蛋有咩微妙既關係","createTime":"2019-05-20T05:23:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T06:01:24.000Z","uid":36563,"like":4,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"42cfa7694a3be90c26553f1ceb121d24e60794ec","tid":1162792,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T05:23:53.000Z","msg":"岩岩去買lunch, 叫左雪菜米粉加煎蛋,<br />\n去佢轉炒蛋, 個呀姐就話因為落雨炒唔到蛋<br />\n全能既連登仔可唔可以話我知到底有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a680828313ab50b87c54db2efae7100e32edd265","tid":1162792,"uid":214692,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T05:24:49.000Z","msg":"問下佢有冇百事"},{"pid":"1e77c424f4490ab4ac8f531dfd1952c491d580b2","tid":1162792,"uid":7406,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T05:29:46.000Z","msg":"炒蛋唔可以返炒又返炒"},{"pid":"7867c152262c880d7629ef4f5bde313ae0f9b63d","tid":1162792,"uid":228963,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T05:30:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b357ef53fab4096801943472d967575fbf467526","tid":1162792,"uid":208235,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T05:31:43.000Z","msg":"痴線 落雨叫炒蛋傻撚咗呀？"},{"pid":"0540f3e99c1ba09baec68963cabf8390ea52ddc2","tid":1162792,"uid":33711,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T05:35:56.000Z","msg":"落雨點撚樣炒蛋啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不如你講嚟聽吓"},{"pid":"8c06a8f395c72bbc6235f911be31eda97005cd51","tid":1162792,"uid":42533,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T05:37:55.000Z","msg":"落雨叫炒蛋 你真係未死過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個阿姐唔斬你都算係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50c8d000f9f53d904e91acc656eeff862a0bd660","tid":1162792,"uid":60279,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T05:38:51.000Z","msg":"其實好無聊好悶<br />\n玩到爛"},{"pid":"8fcf48a09fed4e59246313249a60564ca54eaba2","tid":1162792,"uid":201299,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T05:41:10.000Z","msg":"見你咁白癡就答下你啦<br />\n眾所週知 蛋有不同煮法 但最正宗同最原始既蛋就一定係太陽蛋 顧名思義 呢隻係要太陽下先整到既蛋 利用太陽既熱力，整熟隻蛋<br />\n<br />\n但之後陸陸續續有其他蛋煮法出現 好似炒，蒸等等<br />\n<br />\n炒蛋要用滾油，落雨會有水花 水同油因為磁通量完全唔同 兩者因為粒子性質唔同而彈開 又稱彈油 普通人一掂到輕則毀容，重則甩皮 風險極高 所以一般餐廳都唔會比員工以身犯險落雨去煮呢道菜<br />\n<br />\n有雨落炒蛋供應既餐廳只有少數 而且細佬有幸食過一次<br />\n<br />\n個種回甘真係難以忘懷..."},{"pid":"15675301517cff5807a867c8aa1502da1e5655e6","tid":1162792,"uid":185066,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T05:45:28.000Z","msg":"無知果然好可怕"},{"pid":"13c34b33b68fd099ba3e83a1e146af0187b303a7","tid":1162792,"uid":118623,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T05:46:18.000Z","msg":"00後係唔識呢啲 放過樓主"},{"pid":"fbce6ce792099f43d15e3ef035de8f6069619094","tid":1162792,"uid":69741,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T05:48:25.000Z","msg":"落雨有雨水呀，d蛋漿邊成型啫，點炒都水汪汪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ffdbce05eb26b70fd8df9e116e87af2bd2e9ee9","tid":1162792,"uid":69741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fbce6ce792099f43d15e3ef035de8f6069619094","tid":1162792,"uid":69741,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T05:48:25.000Z","msg":"落雨有雨水呀，d蛋漿邊成型啫，點炒都水汪汪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T05:48:55.000Z","msg":"要食蛋就食煎蛋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2f34fe41248a0e50ecbf1100fe33817be951bbf","tid":1162792,"uid":39326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42cfa7694a3be90c26553f1ceb121d24e60794ec","tid":1162792,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T05:23:53.000Z","msg":"岩岩去買lunch, 叫左雪菜米粉加煎蛋,<br />\n去佢轉炒蛋, 個呀姐就話因為落雨炒唔到蛋<br />\n全能既連登仔可唔可以話我知到底有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":